snippet.title: Nested Lands Gameplay Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
We have officially announced the upcoming release of Nested Lands, a new survival RPG in a harsh medieval atmosphere. 

Get a taste of plague-ravaged life in the gameplay teaser!

💾 Wishlist Nested Lands on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2553040/Nested_Lands/
📩 Leave your email to secure your place in the Alpha test and receive exclusive bonuses after release: https://www.nestedlands.com/
📌 Join our Discord server for exclusive news, arts and activities: https://discord.gg/nestedlands
